{"tid":2400002,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)星河戰隊1-3 CG版1-2","createTime":"2021-02-08T14:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T17:48:02.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"216c67db4f159d1745263e0dd448e8c4eb2d9970","tid":2400002,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">支肺已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=eb7e9ecb\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=7d41d352\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=107ac8cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n1.故事講述在23世紀，人類與外星昆蟲間的星際戰爭。在地球向外星昆蟲宣戰的一年前，Johnny Rico於布宜諾斯艾利斯就讀高中，期間與另一女同學Carmen相戀。在高中畢業後，Johnny的父親希望兒子升讀哈佛大學，但Johnny眼見Carmen投考軍校，為了追求Carmen，Johnny惟有跟從。軍校根據他們的學業成績，Johnny被編往步兵隊，而Carmen則被編入飛行學校。受訓期間，一位名為Dizzy的高中女同學，同為Johnny在校橄欖球隊的戰術教練，對Johnny仰慕多時，也加入了步兵隊。Carmen成績優異..<br />\n<br />\n2.在虫族突襲布宜諾斯艾利斯之後，聯邦軍隊發動反攻，在坦戈約裡擊潰虫族，並在P行星虜獲虫族首領。在此之後，聯邦軍隊乘勝追擊，派大軍殺向虫族隔離區。殘酷的戰鬥沒有止境，機動部隊第6戰隊遭到虫族圍攻，苦盼救援部隊不得，眼看滅亡在即。關鍵時刻，第6戰隊首領夏普德將軍（埃德&middot;勞特Ed Lauter 飾）與幾名士兵吸引虫族，命令霍頓（Jason-Shane Scott 飾）、珊蒂餘下的戰士前往最近的祖魯角哨站避難..<br />\n<br />\n3.一晃十年過去，地球人和虫族的戰爭如火如荼，愈演愈烈。某日，空軍元帥奧瑪&middot;阿諾克（斯蒂芬&middot;霍根Stephen Hogan飾）來地球人的遠方農場羅庫山視察，時任上校的 強尼&middot;瑞哥（加斯帕&middot;範&middot;迪恩Casper Van Dien飾）陪同視察。在此期間，阿諾克的心智被蟲王操控，他切斷了隔離區的電力，使基地完全失去保護。 是夜，虫族對隔離區發動總攻，地球軍雖頑強抵抗，終因寡不敵眾而告敗，基地淪陷。阿諾克則和一干心腹逃離，飛船迫降在OM-1行星。包括負責人斯蓋&middot;馬歇爾 ，飛行員羅拉&middot;貝克等人在內，都被困在星球上無法脫身..<br />\n<br />\n4.電影中這隊機動步兵先是前往一顆小行星救援卡爾將軍（Carl），但卻被星艦拋棄，最終在原小行星基地守衛小隊幫助下登上另一艘突擊星艦離開並炸毀行星基地，但最初的星艦卻被卡爾帶來的蟲后控制。兩支小隊最後合兵一處<br />\n<br />\n5.【星艦戰將】系列的主角強尼瑞克(卡斯伯范戴恩 配音)被降級並調職至火星，而聯邦的艦隊則移動至蟲族的母星準備發動進攻。但就在艦隊遠離火星後，蟲族便開往火星發動了奇襲戰，強尼必須在沒有聯邦艦隊的支援下，指揮新兵抵擋蟲族入侵<br />\n<br />\n10 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=0eafd3c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=b896a97a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野"},{"pid":"317a11c6bd5419ead0b7ec6615ebee7b5f9f38bb","tid":2400002,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/df/Starship_Troopers_-_movie_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fdf%2FStarship_Troopers_-_movie_poster.jpg&h=49b846a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e76bb7330eb883e15756e0fd0897c957905b7e4f","tid":2400002,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bb95ea9cadeaae5838939ffb03737655500f36","tid":2400002,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f906f556cf9fcfd7cbc48260cabacccaf4a9a4e8","tid":2400002,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T17:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}